Paul Bakewell, 35, proposed to partner Tara Barber, 32 , on the A34 in Walsall, West Mids . 
  He secretly designed a poster to be placed on the 20ft-tall and 30ft-wide billboard . 
  Tara was driven to the billboard by her boss who pretended they were going to a business meeting . 
  Paul then got down on one knee and asked her to marry him . 
  The billboard was on the side of the road and featured pictures of the couple . 
 